      <para id="id1170630315249">LEARNING OUTCOME 1: HISTORICAL ENQUIRY- The learner will be able to use enquiry skills to investigate the past and present</para>
      <para id="id1170629457826">1.1 Access the sources</para>
      <para id="id1170635638408">Start asking additional questions on events, artefacts, places, people. They vary in degree of difficulty.</para>
      <para id="id1170624345450">1.2 Use the sources</para>
