      <para id="id1170632072973">Know which sources (books) on specific topics contain information for an assignment / exhibition.</para>
      <para id="id1170630079895">1.3 Communicate information from sources (reporting)</para>
      <para id="id1170629560400">Able to explain information on a diagram, map, chart, sketch</para>
      <para id="id1170628735131">Able to explain an event from the past orally or in writing.</para>
